            </p>
            <a href="/moovey/blogs" class="carouselLink duration-1000 text-pink-700 text-sm border-b border-transparent hover:border-current hover:shadow-md hover:scale-x-110 transform transition-all my-2 mx-auto block w-max text-center font-special capitalize">our reviews</a>
        </article>
        <article class="carousel my-6 border-b p-2">
            <h2 class="font-special capitalize tracking-wider text-pink-600 font-light text-xl text-left my-4 flex items-center justify-start md:text-2xl">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path></svg>
